                        <p><strong>Use Your Phone's Camera:</strong> Start by taking photos of birds you encounter. This helps you document sightings and review details later.</p>
                        <p><strong>Zoom Carefully:</strong> Use digital zoom sparingly to maintain image clarity. Getting physically closer (without disturbing the bird) often yields better results.</p>
